.card_cent >>> .ivu-card-body
    width 100%
    height 100%
.card_box
    width 100%
    height 100%
    display flex
    align-items: center
    justify-content: center
    padding: 25px
    box-sizing: border-box
    border-radius: 4px
    .card_box_img
        width 48px
        height 48px
        border-radius: 50%
        overflow: hidden
        margin-right: 20px
        img
            width 100%
            height 100%
    .card_box_txt
        .sp1
            display block
            color #252631
            font-size 24px
        .sp2
            display block
            color #98A9BC
            font-size 12px
